Dorian Healy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorian_Healy 0 Dorian Healy (born 11 February 1962) is a British actor, best known for his role as Cpt/Maj Kieran Voce in the award-winning drama series Soldier Soldier (1993–1994). He conceived and co-wrote the TV series Masculine Mescaline with Soldier Soldier co-star Gary Love (Sgt Tony Wilton).
